25/05/2011
PRISTINA, Kosovo -- EULEX has established initial contacts with Council of Europe (CoE) rapporteur Dick Marty to discuss his allegations of human organ trafficking by the Kosovo Liberation Army. Mission chief Xavier Bout de Marnhac said on Tuesday (May 24th) that he has asked Marty for details regarding his allegations and will co-operate closely in the future. De Marnhac commented while observing excavation work EULEX is conducting at a suspected mass grave in a village near Vushtrri/Vucitrn. (Kohavision, Klan Kosova, Telegrafi, RTK - 24/05/11)
